b'Human Subjects Research (IRB)'
b'Defining Human Subject Research'
b'Human Subject Research is federally regulated to insure protection for all human subjects. The Institutional Review Board (IRB #00000616) of the University of Illinois College of Medicine at Rockford has a separate Federalwide Assurance (FWA #00005607),from U. S. Department of Health and Human Services (HHS), Office for Human Research Protections (OHRP), and reviews all human subjects\xe2\x80\x99 protocols conducted on or by faculty and students associated with the COM-R.'
